#: Game.Levels.CountingTypes
msgid "# Counting Types: Concrete Computations\n"
"\n"
"You've mastered the composition rules for ¬ß0:\n"
"\n"
"| Principle | Lemma | Formula |\n"
"|---|---|---|\n"
"| Base (Fin) | ¬ß1 | ¬ß2 |\n"
"| Base (Bool) | ¬ß3 | ¬ß4 |\n"
"| Multiplication | ¬ß5 | ¬ß6 |\n"
"| Addition | ¬ß7 | ¬ß8 |\n"
"| Exponentiation | ¬ß9 | ¬ß10 |\n"
"| Equivalence | ¬ß11 | ¬ß12 |\n"
"\n"
"In this world, you'll apply these abstract rules to **concrete finite\n"
"types** and see what the numbers mean:\n"
"\n"
