"In both cases, ¬ß10 βÄî either directly or via ¬ß11.\n"
"\n"
"**Backward** (¬ß12): If ¬ß13, choose ¬ß14.\n"
"\n"
"Note: ¬ß15 is disabled for this level to ensure you practice the\n"
"manual asymmetric proof structure.\n"
"\n"
