"and handles the impossible branches automatically. You'll unlock it\n"
"later.\n"
"\n"
"Fun fact: ¬ß21 is equivalent to ¬ß22 βÄî both have exactly two\n"
"elements. Where ¬ß23 has ¬ß24 and ¬ß25, ¬ß26 has ¬ß27 and ¬ß28.\n"
"\n"
"**A note on ¬ß29**: You used ¬ß30 here for a *bound violation*\n"
