msgid "# The Middle-to-Top Bridge: Multiset.toFinset\n"
"\n"
"You've seen ¬ß0 βÄî the direct list-to-finset conversion.\n"
"But the abstraction ladder has a middle layer too: ¬ß1.\n"
"\n"
"The function ¬ß2 converts a multiset to a finset\n"
"by removing duplicates. The key membership lemma:\n"
"\n"
"¬ß3\n"
"\n"
"This is the multiset analogue of ¬ß4. An element\n"
"belongs to ¬ß5 if and only if it appears in ¬ß6.\n"
"\n"
"The full path up the ladder:\n"
"¬ß7\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Given ¬ß8 for a multiset ¬ß9, prove\n"
"¬ß10."
