#: Game.Levels.SummationFormulas.L11_Factorial
msgid "# The Factorial as a Product\n"
"\n"
"In the previous level, you computed a specific factorial value using\n"
"the recursive definition. Now you'll prove the general connection\n"
"between the factorial and big-operator products:\n"
"\n"
"¬ß0\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Prove this product-to-factorial connection by induction,\n"
"using ¬ß1/¬ß2 (from the constant-product level)\n"
"and ¬ß3/¬ß4 (from the previous level).\n"
"\n"
"**Note**: In Level 10, ¬ß5 was disabled to force you to unfold the\n"
"factorial step by step. Here, ¬ß6 is available again βÄî the base case\n"
"¬ß7 is definitionally true, and you've already learned the\n"
"recursive structure."
msgstr ""

