msgid "Congratulations βÄî you've completed **Finset Operations**!\n"
"\n"
"You proved De Morgan's second law for sets:\n"
"¬ß0.\n"
"\n"
"The forward direction required the most sophisticated use of\n"
"¬ß1 yet: you assumed the *entire disjunction* was false,\n"
