#: Game.Levels.FinNavigation.L16_Boss
msgid "Congratulations βÄî you've completed **Fin Navigation**!\n"
"\n"
"**The Decomposition** (Part 1): Every element of ¬ß0 is\n"
"either ¬ß1 or ¬ß2 for some ¬ß3. This\n"
"is the ¬ß4 analog of: every natural number ¬ß5 either\n"
