"| ¬ß33 | Maximum element of ¬ß34 | ¬ß35 |\n"
"| ¬ß36 | Embed into larger type (same value) | ¬ß37 |\n"
"| ¬ß38 | Move forward by 1 | ¬ß39 |\n"
"\n"
"And the proof recipes:\n"
"\n"
"| Recipe | Pattern |\n"
"|---|---|\n"
"| Compare ¬ß40 values | val lemmas + ¬ß41 |\n"
"| Prove ¬ß42 equality | ¬ß43 + val lemmas |\n"
"| Prove ¬ß44 inequality | ¬ß45 + val lemmas at ¬ß46 + ¬ß47 |\n"
"| Prove injectivity | ¬ß48 + val lemmas at ¬ß49 + ¬ß50 + ¬ß51 or ¬ß52 |\n"
"| Identify as ¬ß53 | ¬ß54 |\n"
