#: Game.Levels.CountingTypes.L08_CountingInjections
msgid "# Injections and the Falling Factorial\n"
"\n"
"An **injection** (or **embedding**) ¬ß0 is a function\n"
"where distinct inputs always give distinct outputs βÄî no two elements\n"
"of ¬ß1 map to the same element of ¬ß2.\n"
"\n"
"How many injections are there from ¬ß3 to ¬ß4? For the first\n"
